You can upload unique gifs and change your username in real time to suit your mood! You can have four distinct images to reflect how you feel about a certain song that's being played.

Simplify Controller is a small handy assistant for our desktop application Simplify for Spotify, Rdio, iTunes and Vox music players. 

Simplify Controller allows you remotely switch tracks, change volume, toggle playback state, view current song that is playing on any local computer with Simplify for Spotify, Rdio, iTunes and Vox music players installed.

Simple to use—launch Simplify for Spotify, Rdio, iTunes and Vox music players and start music playback on the computer you want to control, then launch Simplify Controller on your iOS device and select machine you want to control.

If you have multiple players launched, you can switch between all the desktop and web-players detected by Simplify on iMac or Macbook.
